Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 13), dkms

Package: nexus-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dkms (>= 2.1.0.0), linux-headers-generic | linux-headers
Description: DKMS version for the nexus IPC for V\OS
 Nexus provides an improved BeOS-style IPC primitives (ports, semaphores,
 areas, node monitoring) as a Linux kernel module. This package uses
 DKMS to build the module for the running kernel automatically.
